Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.39,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6E3C42&}Re:{\c&H060200&}從零開始的休息時間~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我真的讀不懂這些文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,昴你真有點不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:14.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,明明既沒有錢又看不懂文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼來到露格尼卡的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為...該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:23.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個啦 就像SF輕小說一樣穿越到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:29.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這種情況也是存在的 這世上充滿了戲劇性...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.61,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,你要是這麼突然問的話 我也只能不同意你說的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:36.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何這些東西的名稱跟我老家的比較像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:41.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,沒準習慣了就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的是非常像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:47.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,比如說這蘋果 RINGA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.96,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(350,70)}看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,在我老家稱為 RINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:51.09,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(350,70)}蘋  果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.27,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,RIN...GO？好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說RINGA的發音才是怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:58.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,發音總有一些違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:01.98,SignB,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50os(350,70)}蘋  果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:02.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,想發出RIN!ga的聲音 就是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:01.98,SignC,Text,0000,0000,0000,,口音!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:03.08,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,RINGA~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.68,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,有種要高潮了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:12.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,總之這裡就有一種很像但又不是的特點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:16.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇...這裡明明是水果店為什麼會賣青椒（pi-man）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:19.79,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord1\pos(293,80)\1c&H5A12CA&\3c&H5800B0&\b0}青 椒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:21.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這裡叫pi-maru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,果然發音很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:25.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.29,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:31.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你很討厭pi-man...啊不 討厭pi-maru嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,o(*////▽////*)q
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:34.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,欸︿(￣︶￣)︿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:36.65,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,因為那可是pimaru啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是綠色的惡魔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,綠色的惡魔...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:43.89,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,絕大多數我是能吃的 真的 真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:46.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,但是只吃青椒不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就只能抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.76,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,挑食可是不好的哦 莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:55.47,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,帕克 我也有努力過的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.60,italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}這種孩子氣...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.36,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一次遇到青椒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.16,italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}再加上這種全力狡辯的性格...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}青椒對我抱有極大的敵意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.65,italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}真是可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:03.79,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 昴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不愛吃青椒這種事有那麼奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:11.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,沒 我覺得人討厭一兩種東西是沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.63,italics,SUbaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}嘛 我也不愛吃青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:17.80,italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}還有番茄啊茄子啊蔓菁之類很多都不想吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.01,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,一臉無奈樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然對我失望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:25.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 才不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:27.18,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,喏 那副無奈臉不就是很失望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,帕克 不要說些奇怪的話啊！
